1
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:09,739
As the chief technology
ambassador for Minghui Group,

2
00:00:09,740 --> 00:00:11,059
I'd like to invite you,

3
00:00:11,060 --> 00:00:12,619
the press, to join me in witnessing

4
00:00:12,620 --> 00:00:15,540
the latest research results
from Qingniao and Minghui Lab.

5
00:00:16,060 --> 00:00:17,380
Please, follow me.

6
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:23,740
Thank you for your concern.

7
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:27,820
Minghui Group has
weathered a century of change.

8
00:00:28,060 --> 00:00:31,059
We once faced a critical choice

9
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,420
amidst the waves of the times,

10
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:37,620
and we invested everything
into a biotech company.

11
00:00:37,740 --> 00:00:40,499
Now, with Qingniao Group on board,

12
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:44,459
the industrial synergy
between Minghui and Spark

13
00:00:44,460 --> 00:00:47,259
will revitalize
Minghui's technology sector.

14
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:50,099
More importantly, it marks
the realization of an independent

15
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:55,060
and controllable industrial ecosystem
for our tech enterprises in key areas.

16
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:02,459
Hello, Lawyer Fang.

17
00:01:02,460 --> 00:01:05,499
Regarding Yinghai Group's
unilateral termination

18
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,419
due to unforeseen
compliance risk clauses,

19
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:09,139
concerning Qingniao Group's
technical supply,

20
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:11,780
as their representative,
what is your response?

21
00:01:16,420 --> 00:01:19,459
In response to Yinghai Group's
malicious breach of contract

22
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:22,299
and Raymond Technology's
abuse of market dominance,

23
00:01:22,300 --> 00:01:25,539
we have begun collecting
and securing evidence.

24
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:28,620
We will fully protect
our client's legal rights.

25
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:32,220
We also hope that Yinghai Group
and Raymond Technology

26
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:34,679
can face the seriousness of the issue.

27
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,879
=Echoes of Gang City=

28
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:42,080
=Episode 25=
(I'm Waiting for You in Gang City)

29
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:46,860
Come on.

30
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:49,900
To your complete victory.

31
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,340
Because of you.

32
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:14,459
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

33
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:15,900
A total victory!

34
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:17,180
Wait a second.

35
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:20,059
A video call from our spokesperson.

36
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:21,740
- Hello, Best Actress Su.
- Hello, Best Actress Su.

37
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:24,340
Hi, everyone!

38
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:28,300
You won't be able to taste
our victory wine, will you?

39
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:30,859
Don't just pick on me.

40
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:32,900
Why didn't you video call them?

41
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:35,099
I only called you.

42
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,179
I just wanted to call you.

43
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,419
Do you have time now?

44
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:38,540
Can we talk privately...

45
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:08,670
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

46
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:09,980
Alright.

47
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:13,140
Don't drink any more.

48
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:21,960
♪You turn and look back at me♪

49
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:28,530
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

50
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:35,100
