51
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:41,840
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

52
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:48,280
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

53
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:55,260
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

54
00:03:55,630 --> 00:04:02,600
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

55
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:08,420
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

56
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:15,449
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

57
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:18,329
♪The promise we made♪

58
00:04:18,330 --> 00:04:22,019
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

59
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:28,599
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

60
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:35,010
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

61
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:41,739
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

62
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:46,830
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

63
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:50,330
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪

64
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:10,579
There's such a huge
breakthrough with the Minghui project,

65
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:12,100
so why didn't you tell me sooner?

66
00:05:21,940 --> 00:05:23,420
Mr. Raymond,

67
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:25,940
