the contract with them?

70
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,940
And you're here asking me, huh?

71
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:37,179
Do you know,

72
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:38,499
so far,

73
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:43,900
