himself in the business world.

82
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,500
Is it not?

83
00:06:19,820 --> 00:06:23,300
Qingniao's legal department
has filed an anti-monopoly lawsuit.

84
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:37,180
Mr. Raymond,

85
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:41,380
