86
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:50,980
You're not the only one
who has to handle a crisis now.

87
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:59,180
The matter hasn't been resolved yet.

88
00:06:59,380 --> 00:07:02,500
You can't leave.

89
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:08,540
What's your attitude?

90
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,300
Mr. Shen,

91
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:15,180
