any of our problems.

94
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:28,700
Let go.

95
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:33,940
I said let go!

96
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:36,179
We've already lost.

97
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,779
This isn't over yet.

98
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,819
How do you know we've lost?

99
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:40,459
Let go!

100
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,379
A loss is a loss.

101
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:44,019
You lost!

102
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:45,500
What about me?

103
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:49,300
Dad!

104
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,820
Dad!

105
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,470
Dad!

106
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:58,379
Someone, help!

107
00:07:58,380 --> 00:08:01,900
Someone, help!

108
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,420
Why don't you stay one more day?

109
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:04,780
We can go back together tomorrow.

110
00:08:04,980 --> 00:08:06,859
After the press conference,

111
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,780
