112
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,580
I can't leave it all to Grandfather.

113
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:17,899
I'm going back tomorrow.

114
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:19,100
Call me when you arrive.

115
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:24,140
I'll be waiting for you at home.

116
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:30,500
Alright, I'm off.

117
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,060
Goodbye.

118
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,220
See you in Gang City.

119
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:55,300
